flowchart TD
    A["Start: Query with WHERE on non-leading index column(s)"]
    B["Multicolumn B-Tree Index Exists (e.g., (col1, col2, col3))"]
    A --> B

    C{Is PostgreSQL version 11+?}
    B --> C

    C -->|No| D[Index cannot be used; full scan or other index]
    C -->|Yes| E{"Is query using IS NULL, IN, or skipping values on leading column(s)?"}

    E -->|No| F[Standard index scan not possible; consider query rewrite or additional index]
    E -->|Yes| G[Skip Scan Optimization Activated]

    G --> H["Database engine skips over possible values of leading column(s)"]
    H --> I["Index scan proceeds on specified non-leading column(s)"]
    I --> J[Efficient retrieval of matching rows]

    D --> K[Query performance may be suboptimal]
    F --> K
    J --> L[End]
    K --> L
